The People of the State of New York ex rel. Jose Tormos et al., against Commissioner of Welfare of the City of New York et al.

Motion by New York Foundling Hospital to dismiss appeal granted unless the appellants procure the record on appeal and appellants’ points to be served and filed on or before January 21, 1960, with notice of argument for February 2, 1960, said appeal to be argued or submitted when reached. Concur — Botein, P. J., Breitel, M. M. Frank, Valente and Stevens, JJ.
